{"tid":138899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伍婉婷死撐非針對巴士","createTime":"2017-03-01T03:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T12:43:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c6f0954dbb126341f548e86733466dcd9b5ce8f","tid":138899,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:44:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19943449&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170301&amp;mobile=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19943449%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170301%26mobile%3D1&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=a837059a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19943449%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170301%26mobile%3D1&h=b528c00b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19943449&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170301&amp;mobile=1</a><br />\n<br />\n伍婉婷死撐非針對巴士<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n運輸署建議將崇光外巴士站前禁區定為全面禁止的士上落客，並延長禁區時間至午夜12時。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】巴士被抄牌事件引起軒然大波，被指是事件始作俑者的區議員伍婉婷，因早前曾在區議會批評巴士司機未停正站觸發事件而捱批。昨會議上她率先發言，但未提任何建議前便先為自己澄清，強調早前發言並無要求當局針對巴士執法。<br />\n伍又在會上要求警方交代上月票控巴士司機的原因，以及坊間流傳針對巴士的執法行動是否屬實，似希望借警方的解釋為針對自己的指控解畫。其後警方澄清從未針對巴士的執法行動，她隨即駁斥坊間的流言有誤，但警方以案件已進入司法程序為由拒透露票控案情。<br />\n<br />\n與楊雪盈爆罵戰<br />\n<br />\n伍又在會上不點名暗批另一區議員楊雪盈，指有人稱銅鑼灣居民的意見罔顧公眾安全，聲稱要維護本區居民利益，「還他們一個公道」。楊雪盈反駁指伍的言論純屬猜想，要求她收回言論，但伍未有收回，反再次多花發言時間反駁楊。<br />\n■記者：鍾雅宜<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n崇光巴士站擬擴禁區範圍站前禁區時間延長　的士不准上落客<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;5小時前"},{"pid":"fbe8a02835b701a9b7b6dc3f3aeb03879e71a3df","tid":138899,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:48:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc20a71a73f613de324d41a652c25b30de3ea313","tid":138899,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:21:37.000Z","msg":"唔知醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  夠膽講唔夠膽認<br />\n講野唔經大腦<br />\n事後唔負責任<br />\n個個月淨係識出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6db9aa2ebefc49fda6c4446b1594fcd01abedd","tid":138899,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:34:34.000Z","msg":"有晒錄音都唔認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f090c50ff4263a85f39ddf9207ceb7ce618c03fe","tid":138899,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9480ff2ce5bd0eacb652efdd514f066d227f6237","tid":138899,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:41:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/01/194825_1377f4fd11fdb1664b0b8f2a6c9c3d44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F01%2F194825_1377f4fd11fdb1664b0b8f2a6c9c3d44.jpg&h=454ff800&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nDc9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6b08e78e0c09f75cd6231f4f241c27b72fe72d","tid":138899,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:43:51.000Z","msg":"仲要賴楊雪盈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}